# Codex Writer Summary

## Files changed
- `pages/Profile/base/profile.jsx`

## Main fixes
- Reset `isMountedRef.current` on mount so the unmount guard remains reliable across effect cleanup/remount cycles.
- Guarded `handleSave()` entry against running after unmount.
- Reused a trimmed full-name value through the save flow and kept all post-await `setState` calls behind the mounted check.
- Cleared and nulled the save-status timeout before reuse and during cleanup to avoid stale idle-state updates after unmount.

## Tests or checks run
- Reviewed the scoped `git diff` for `pages/Profile/base/profile.jsx`.
- Ran `git diff --check` for `pages/Profile/base/profile.jsx`.
- Inspected the updated handler and cleanup sections directly in the worktree.
- Checked for local formatter/linter availability; no repo-local JS tooling or package manifest was present in this worktree.

## Follow-up risk
- No automated UI test covers this save/unmount path here, so the change is verified by code inspection rather than by an executable frontend test.
